Israel CRUZ, petitioner,
v.
UNITED STATES. No. 13-6821. Supreme Court of the United States Nov. 18, 2013. Case below, 506 Fed.Appx. 945 . Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eleventh Circuit denied. Justice KAGAN took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
